data.description: This Mt.Juliet home has it all! This pristine 5 bedroom/4 bath home has 4 of the bedrooms on the main floor. (see floor plan in photos) Beautiful customized finishes are implemented throughout the home. The incredible outdoor living area will blow you away! It includes a 30'x14' heated saltwater pool, 8'x8' heated spa, a privacy fenced yard, a pergola, lots of custom hardscape and landscaping. There is a Rain Bird full yard irrigation system, security cameras, and a Ring doorbell. Come and see how truly special this home is!
